Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是它不是已經...
